  <steps>
    <step num="0">Mix the macaroni, water, and salt in a microwaveable mug. </step>
    <step num="1">Microwave for 2-3 minutes, then stir. </step>
    <step num="2">Add the milk, cheese, salt, and pepper, then stir. </step>
